snippet.title: Project Colored Mountains | Demo Release Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2340980/Project_Colored_Mountains
The demo for my 3D platformer, Project Colored Mountains, is out now on Steam! I will be participating in the February 5th-12th Next Fest and at some point during it livestreaming the development of the game. Music by @Pianomations.
